{
  "video_id": "12kN2a_VTJg",
  "title": "電影經典台詞#8【高年級實習生】// The Intern Movie Spotlight",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 890.0,
      "text": "Hello, I'm Crown"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 890.0,
      "end_time": 3732.0,
      "text": "Today we'll be talking about some classic lines from the movie \"The Intern\"!"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 8893.0,
      "end_time": 13543.0,
      "text": "Last week we talked about the lines from \"Me Before You\", which you guys strongly recommended"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 13543.0,
      "end_time": 17503.0,
      "text": "This time we are going to talk about \"The Intern\", which is"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 17503.0,
      "end_time": 19633.0,
      "text": "nominated every time in the comment section"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 19633.0,
      "end_time": 22433.0,
      "text": "\"The Intern\" is a movie from late last year"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 22433.0,
      "end_time": 25334.0,
      "text": "And the main characters are the well-known"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 25334.0,
      "end_time": 27384.0,
      "text": "Anne Hathaway and Robert de Niro"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 27384.0,
      "end_time": 30724.0,
      "text": "I believe we were all very curious about how this mysterious combination"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 30724.0,
      "end_time": 33693.0,
      "text": "bring out their wonderful performance"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 33693.0,
      "end_time": 36874.0,
      "text": "There are also some great, useful lines in this movie"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 36874.0,
      "end_time": 38624.0,
      "text": "so let's check them out!"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 39254.0,
      "end_time": 40055.0,
      "text": "I read once"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 40055.0,
      "end_time": 41715.0,
      "text": "“Musicians don’t retire"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 41715.0,
      "end_time": 43784.0,
      "text": "they stop when there’s no more music in them.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 43784.0,
      "end_time": 48264.0,
      "text": "Well, I still have music in me, absolutely positive about that!"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 51816.0,
      "end_time": 54646.0,
      "text": "我心中還有音樂，這點毋庸置疑"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 54646.0,
      "end_time": 56206.0,
      "text": "The previous quote"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 56206.0,
      "end_time": 59867.0,
      "text": "“Musicians don’t retire, they stop when there’s no more music in them.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 59867.0,
      "end_time": 63367.0,
      "text": "is from Louis Armstrong, the American Jazz Musician."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 63367.0,
      "end_time": 65717.0,
      "text": "Well I think it's quite beautiful so I mentioned it here"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 65717.0,
      "end_time": 68717.0,
      "text": "Ben wanted to say that, if he were a musician"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 68717.0,
      "end_time": 72886.0,
      "text": "and there is still great music in his heart making him continue"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 72886.0,
      "end_time": 76858.0,
      "text": "It means that he still has many inspirations and things he want to do in his life"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 76858.0,
      "end_time": 80046.0,
      "text": "so he wish to achieve them by an internship"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 80046.0,
      "end_time": 82006.0,
      "text": "\"Absolutely\" means 完全、絕對"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 82006.0,
      "end_time": 86277.0,
      "text": "while \"positive\" is 正面、正向, which means 確定、相信"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 86817.0,
      "end_time": 88907.0,
      "text": "Hi, Jules"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 88907.0,
      "end_time": 91228.0,
      "text": "I’m Ben, your new intern"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 91228.0,
      "end_time": 93867.0,
      "text": "I’m glad you also see the humor in this"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 93867.0,
      "end_time": 95138.0,
      "text": "It'll be hard not to"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 100858.0,
      "end_time": 103048.0,
      "text": "我是 Ben，你的新實習生"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 103048.0,
      "end_time": 105728.0,
      "text": "很高興你也覺得這事挺滑稽的"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 105728.0,
      "end_time": 107218.0,
      "text": "很難不這麼覺得"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 107218.0,
      "end_time": 108498.0,
      "text": "We usually think that"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 108498.0,
      "end_time": 112658.0,
      "text": "interns are young people who learn social experience by going to companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 112658.0,
      "end_time": 115168.0,
      "text": "But Ben, as an experienced person"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 115168.0,
      "end_time": 119939.0,
      "text": "was assigned as a private intern to the company founder, Jules"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 119939.0,
      "end_time": 123950.0,
      "text": "Both Jules and Ben thought this situation was funny"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 123950.0,
      "end_time": 127489.0,
      "text": "The \"humour\" in \"See the humor in this\" means 幽默"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 127489.0,
      "end_time": 130780.0,
      "text": "If you want to say 「你這個人很幽默風趣」"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 130780.0,
      "end_time": 133269.0,
      "text": "you can say \"you have a good sense of humor”"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 133269.0,
      "end_time": 136596.0,
      "text": "\"it’ll be hard not to\" means「很難不去這樣做」"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 136596.0,
      "end_time": 140340.0,
      "text": "which means \"any one would think its ridiculous if they saw this situation\""
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 140973.0,
      "end_time": 141960.0,
      "text": "W...why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 141960.0,
      "end_time": 145930.0,
      "text": "Erm, what, am I too inexperienced at running a business?"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 145930.0,
      "end_time": 147270.0,
      "text": "I...I didn't go to Harvard?"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 147270.0,
      "end_time": 150050.0,
      "text": "My...my methods aren’t by the book?"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 150050.0,
      "end_time": 151641.0,
      "text": "I mean..."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 151641.0,
      "end_time": 153291.0,
      "text": "isn’t that how we got here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 157511.0,
      "end_time": 160512.0,
      "text": "是說因為我不按牌理出牌才要這樣嗎？"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 160512.0,
      "end_time": 163912.0,
      "text": "但是，我們不就是因為這樣才能有今天的成就嗎？"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 163912.0,
      "end_time": 166218.0,
      "text": "Jules was informed that the investors"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 166218.0,
      "end_time": 169931.0,
      "text": "are hiring a new CEO for the company"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 169931.0,
      "end_time": 173562.0,
      "text": "so she was stunned and sad after she heard the news"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 173562.0,
      "end_time": 175723.0,
      "text": "\"Methods\" means 方法、方式"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 175723.0,
      "end_time": 178112.0,
      "text": "and \"by the book\" is a common usage"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 178112.0,
      "end_time": 181752.0,
      "text": "which means 照章辦事、或是按著規矩行事"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 181752.0,
      "end_time": 184343.0,
      "text": "You can also say “according to the rules\""
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 186307.0,
      "end_time": 186787.0,
      "text": "Hi, honey"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 186787.0,
      "end_time": 187083.0,
      "text": "Hey"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 189193.0,
      "end_time": 190752.0,
      "text": "Over the hump"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 194193.0,
      "end_time": 195442.0,
      "text": "度過難關"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 195442.0,
      "end_time": 197334.0,
      "text": "Though Ben had just joined the company"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 197334.0,
      "end_time": 202054.0,
      "text": "he already noticed the industriousness of Jules"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 202054.0,
      "end_time": 203794.0,
      "text": "so he reminded her"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 203794.0,
      "end_time": 208264.0,
      "text": "to never forget who the credit of bringing this company success belongs to."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 208264.0,
      "end_time": 211074.0,
      "text": "\"Hump\" is 一個隆起來的小圓丘"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 211074.0,
      "end_time": 212975.0,
      "text": "So \"Over the hump\""
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 212975.0,
      "end_time": 215635.0,
      "text": "is successfully stepping over this 小圓丘"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 215635.0,
      "end_time": 218155.0,
      "text": "which means the hardest part is conquered"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 222174.0,
      "end_time": 226085.0,
      "text": "How is it that you always manage to say the right thing..."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 226085.0,
      "end_time": 227156.0,
      "text": "do the right thing..."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 227156.0,
      "end_time": 229345.0,
      "text": "be the right thing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 229345.0,
      "end_time": 231195.0,
      "text": "It’s uncanny."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 237985.0,
      "end_time": 240975.0,
      "text": "為什麼你總是有辦法說出最恰當的話"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 240975.0,
      "end_time": 244307.0,
      "text": "做出最正確的事、當一個最完美的存在呢？"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 244307.0,
      "end_time": 245627.0,
      "text": "真的很不可思議"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 245627.0,
      "end_time": 249017.0,
      "text": "All these shipping problems, website malfunctions"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 249017.0,
      "end_time": 253417.0,
      "text": "and the terrible incident of mistakenly sending the email complaining about mom to her"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 253417.0,
      "end_time": 255808.0,
      "text": "made Jules feel really pressured"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 255808.0,
      "end_time": 258497.0,
      "text": "But Ben could always let her feel better"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 258497.0,
      "end_time": 261188.0,
      "text": "which Jules thought this was wonderful"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 261188.0,
      "end_time": 263798.0,
      "text": "Usually, when we want to say「某人做了某事」"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 263798.0,
      "end_time": 265568.0,
      "text": "we might say, \"do something\""
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 265568.0,
      "end_time": 268418.0,
      "text": "But the “manage to do something” here"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 268418.0,
      "end_time": 271948.0,
      "text": "has a meaning of「他竟然有能力、有辦法可以做到這樣子的事情」"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 273508.0,
      "end_time": 276396.0,
      "text": "They say you can’t put the genie back in the bottle but..."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 276396.0,
      "end_time": 278118.0,
      "text": "we can try, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 283377.0,
      "end_time": 288059.0,
      "text": "人們說，覆水難收，但是我們可以試試看，對嗎？"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 288059.0,
      "end_time": 290449.0,
      "text": "Jules, who wanted to save her marriage and family life"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 290449.0,
      "end_time": 293379.0,
      "text": "had finally made up her mind to hire a CEO"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 293379.0,
      "end_time": 296259.0,
      "text": "Though this made her sad, she still hoped that in the end"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 296259.0,
      "end_time": 299839.0,
      "text": "everything would go back to the happy life it used to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 299839.0,
      "end_time": 304690.0,
      "text": "Basically, we can see \"Genie\" as the one in Aladdin's lamp"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 304690.0,
      "end_time": 308380.0,
      "text": "So the idiom \"Can’t put the genie back in the bottle\" means"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 308380.0,
      "end_time": 311330.0,
      "text": "「已經發生的事情，你沒有辦法挽回」"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 311330.0,
      "end_time": 313500.0,
      "text": "Another idiom similar to"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 313500.0,
      "end_time": 315150.0,
      "text": "\"can’t put the genie back in the bottle\" is"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 315150.0,
      "end_time": 317570.0,
      "text": "\"no use crying over spilt milk”"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 317570.0,
      "end_time": 321369.0,
      "text": "which is 「打翻的牛奶，你再怎麼哭也沒有辦法把它復原」"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 323049.0,
      "end_time": 323940.0,
      "text": "It’s moments like this"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 323940.0,
      "end_time": 326391.0,
      "text": "when you need someone you know you can count on"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 326391.0,
      "end_time": 327391.0,
      "text": "So, thank you"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 333451.0,
      "end_time": 334601.0,
      "text": "就是在這種時候"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 334601.0,
      "end_time": 337781.0,
      "text": "你需要一個你知道你能依靠的人"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 337781.0,
      "end_time": 340322.0,
      "text": "Jules, who had decided to hire a CEO,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 340322.0,
      "end_time": 342402.0,
      "text": "came back to Ben at the last moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 342402.0,
      "end_time": 345491.0,
      "text": "This was because she still hoped to have someone persuading her"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 345491.0,
      "end_time": 349262.0,
      "text": "not to compromise with the situation"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 349262.0,
      "end_time": 351422.0,
      "text": "\"Moments\" can be replaced by \"times\""
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 351422.0,
      "end_time": 354182.0,
      "text": "which also has the meaning of 「時機、時候」"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 354182.0,
      "end_time": 355532.0,
      "text": "\"Can count on\" means"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 355532.0,
      "end_time": 357892.0,
      "text": "「可以相信、可以依靠」"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 357962.0,
      "end_time": 361072.0,
      "text": "All the above are some classic lines in \"The Intern\""
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 361072.0,
      "end_time": 363563.0,
      "text": "Feel free to tell me which one is your favorite!"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 363563.0,
      "end_time": 365742.0,
      "text": "Last but not least, don't forget to leave a comment below"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 365742.0,
      "end_time": 369043.0,
      "text": "and tell me what other movies do you guys want me to talk about"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 371933.0,
      "end_time": 374413.0,
      "text": "If you like this video, please give us a big thumbs up"
    },
    {
